<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>3つのステップ</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">シンプルなルールが、予測不能な体験を生む。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-row">
      <div class="step-card">
        <span class="step-number">01</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">16枚選ぶ</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">写真ライブラリから16枚を選択。あなたの日常から、さまざまな瞬間を。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <span class="step-number">02</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">7枚がランダムに</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">どの7枚が選ばれるかは、あなたにもわからない。偶然が決める。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <span class="step-number">03</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">1日1枚、匿名で届く</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">毎日1枚、友達のフィードに匿名で現れる。誰の写真かは、秘密。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .section-sub {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
  }

  .steps-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .step-card {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .step-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--purple-light) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  .step-connector {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .step-connector {
      padding-top: 0;
      padding-left: 2rem;
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .step-card {
      border-left: 2px solid var(--gray-200);
    }

    .step-card:first-child {
      border-left-color: var(--purple);
    }
  }
</style>
